summary: There are little rocks scattered all across skyrim and they look terrible so i removed them.
descriptionHtml:
Personal
----------------------------------------------------------------
So in Skyrim there are a bunch of tiny rocks that i think look terrible so i removed them.
a friend wanted the file too so i uploaded it here, its really a very simply "mod".

Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------
You know those little rocks along side the road? ya i took em out.

User: Cauug has a mod that does more i recommend you use that
Here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55240/?


Performance
-------------------------------------------------------------------
You may get a small frame boost but it wont be much.
I didn't make this mod to save frame but i certainly wont hurt your frames.

Credit
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Me.
